 <arm>
   <uof name="Procedural_shape_model">
     <description>
The Procedural_shape_model UoF specifies the data structure for the high level description of operations to modify 
shape models by local shape operations. The basic modification operations are defined in the 
application modules which reference this module. This module provides a mechanism for associating a base shape model with the 
shape model  
resulting from the application of a shape modification operation. 
It also provides for the definition of a sequence of modification operations and the association 
of this sequence with of an explicit shape model produced by applying the operations.
  </description>

 
